SETSTATS

NAME
        SetStats()

SYNOPSIS
        mapping SetStats(mapping arg)

DESCRIPTION
        Sets which stats are altered by a potion or bonus, and to what extent.

EXAMPLES
        SetStats( ([ "strength" : 30, "intelligence" : -30 ]) )

LOCATION
        /lib/bonus
/lib/potion


SEE ALSO
        GetStats, SetSkills, GetSkills

Author
        Cratylus

